model

Interface Model

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbsModel, Game2048Model, MazeGameModel

    public interface Model
    The Interface Model. The model is an interface defining the data to be displayed. or otherwise acted upon in the user interface. Every concrete class that implements model must also extend Observable in order to notify the Presenter that something has changed.
